  "description": "A large and roomy Side-by-side refrigerator that combines two full-size compartments for cooling and freezing food in one body. The model was introduced to the market by the Beko brand in 2023, is positioned by the manufacturer in the upper segment of the mid-price range and can serve as an excellent choice for large families. The total useful capacity of the model is 532 liters. There is 347 liters of free space behind the refrigerator door, and up to 185 liters fit in the freezer. The model uses a compressor with patented ProSmart inverter technology. This compressor provides stepless performance control, while reducing operating noise and energy consumption. The Beko GNO 5322 XPN refrigerator creates noise no higher than 39 dB during operation. The model is equipped with an automatic defrosting system. The refrigerator has two circulation circuits, which expands the possibilities for fine-tuning the temperature in the cooling and freezing zones. There is an economical Eco mode, and a separate Vacation program is also available. The control panel has a child lock system, and the operating parameters of the device are displayed on the LED screen. If the door is not closed tightly, an audible alert will sound. Neat hidden handles are used for the door leaves.",
